## 🗃️ **Database Schema (Supabase)**

### **Users Table**

| Field | Type | Description    |
| ----- | ---- | -------------- |
| id    | UUID | unique user id |
| name  | text | user name      |
| email | text | user email     |

### **Transactions Table**

| Field     | Type     | Description              |
| --------- | -------- | ------------------------ |
| id        | UUID     | unique txn id            |
| user_id   | UUID     | FK to users              |
| person    | text     | whom money sent/received |
| amount    | float    | amount value             |
| category  | text     | 'credit' / 'debit'       |
| timestamp | datetime | recorded time            |

### **Tasks Table**

| Field     | Type     | Description    |
| --------- | -------- | -------------- |
| id        | UUID     | unique task id |
| user_id   | UUID     | FK to users    |
| title     | text     | task name      |
| due_date  | datetime | task deadline  |
| completed | boolean  | true/false     |
| reminder  | boolean  | true/false     |

